#: UG9/en/vsan-user-guide.adoc:169
msgid ""
"The VSAN Web UI intentionally offers relatively minimal administration and "
"monitoring capabilities."
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: UG9/en/vsan-user-guide.adoc:171
msgid ""
"One of design philosophies behind VSAN is that, after the setup is "
